{"tid":576754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朝蔣公靈柩潑紅漆 命理師：潑漆者恐發生嚴重下場","createTime":"2018-03-01T07:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T10:14:09.000Z","uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8ff3b8c86e58582c46e824e9df2c670b065c73","tid":576754,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:13:12.000Z","msg":"今天是228紀念日，有獨派民眾闖入桃園慈湖陵寢，朝先總統蔣中正棺柩潑灑紅漆，意圖凸顯歷史事件。不過此舉看在過去精準預言林志玲、言承旭會在去年復合的命理師江嘉葉眼裡卻是相當擔憂，直言這些潑漆者恐怕會發生嚴重下場。<br />\n<br />\n江嘉葉從事發現場照，看見蔣中正靈柩旁有穿著軍服的護衛，很可能是以前的部下，「這些護衛很憤怒，這件事不會就這樣結束。」江嘉葉坦言感受到這些護衛的憤怒，恐怕會找當事者報復。<br />\n<br />\n俗話說敬鬼神而遠之，江嘉葉透露曾有民眾喝醉去墳場亂尿尿，回到家突然暴斃的例子，「有人到你家潑漆已經受不了，更何況那些鬼神，鬼是無形的，要怎麼捉弄你都可以。」<br />\n<br />\n至於這些潑漆者下場會如何？江嘉葉說，端看這些人福報夠不夠，福報多傷害你力量就沒這麼大，若平常不做善事也不捐款，傷害力量也大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/151250_7c8674f6f99c0d59980eba82ba070acf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F151250_7c8674f6f99c0d59980eba82ba070acf.png&h=32d77560&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/151251_c0a1a67683beb24f4f9c1f7c52df1880.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F151251_c0a1a67683beb24f4f9c1f7c52df1880.png&h=b331e06a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45c7b41d4b85fc54d03b0cae9a3b0296443c69d8","tid":576754,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:14:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇橫死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c3613b5a85b074d70d14c8ab87c62ea32d5d72","tid":576754,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"毛匪反而冇人淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係識得欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f408f95e001f1c521b61ba37ee1a17e633185fc","tid":576754,"uid":53794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">精準預言林志玲、言承旭會在去年復合的命理師江嘉葉眼裡卻是相當擔憂</span><br />\n<br />\n屌啲台狗真係弱撚智"},{"pid":"fb55c01a6aee72a4cd8e942db322ad9154b1fc31","tid":576754,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"呃神騙鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3168e4cdeac9a0302948a0ad8d9de68d94caba","tid":576754,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母神棍9up都可以當新聞，我食lunch都可以啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b8caab253d0e52ccd9c80f14bfc6f7df100966","tid":576754,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"為殺人提供解釋"},{"pid":"2353f24a6aa5cfaddd293cf4c48bd82cc09ded13","tid":576754,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c3613b5a85b074d70d14c8ab87c62ea32d5d72","tid":576754,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"毛匪反而冇人淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只係識得欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:20:50.000Z","msg":"關乜嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入都入唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f00df0d8f809a5095f3ed6fbf9c7ed3ce8404c","tid":576754,"uid":20189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3168e4cdeac9a0302948a0ad8d9de68d94caba","tid":576754,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母神棍9up都可以當新聞，我食lunch都可以啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src